data.description:
Looking for a Quality New Construction, One-Level residence, with Acreage in the County and NO HOA?!
Here it is! Included in this fabulous Ranch Home on 1.227 acres is a Double Garage, Granite, SS
Appliances, LVP throughout the main and Carpet in the 3 bedrooms. Enjoy Front and back Covered
Porches for relaxing or grilling out, a side loading garage for convenience, and a backyard that offers a
shared pond. The estimated completion date is September 30th. Seller requires a 45 day extension if
needed and to close at The Brice Law Firm. This location is off the bypass and convenient to Charlotte
and surrounding areas. Plans and Photos are not 100% reflective of the finished product. No Fireplace
added.
